and that all the rebels are unlikely to lay down their weapons and 
move back by mrs chamorros april 25 inauguration the package 
includes about 42 million for contra repatriation and anticontra 
lawmakers likely will want to debate that issue 
leahy accused the administration of having its priorities wrong 
suggesting he might seek to divert some money to help bolster 
