setting newcrop fruit peaches were in goodtoexcellent 
condition in georgia and peach trees were setting fruit in texas 
springlike weather prevailed over floridas major vegetable 
areas and the harvest picked up steam vegetable growth was 
reported to be good in the rio grande valley of texas with 
harvests continuing for carrot cabbage celery and lettuce crops 
