rise about 20 miles downstream near ebro said ginger vance a 
spokeswoman for the washington county civil defense office 
it will be at least thursday before most evacuees can start 
returning to their homes and begin cleaning up said county 
adminstrator roger hagan caryville is a small farming town about 
