the j paul getty museum announced today 
it has purchased its greatest 19th century painting the 
masterpiece irises by dutch artist vincent van gogh for an 
undisclosed sum 
painted in 1889 irises was sold to the museum by alan bond 
the financially troubled australian entrepreneur who paid a record 
