interlinked and theres nothing in it for south africa if there 
is no cuban withdrawal angola and namibia are intimately connected 
by history it was a natural approach 
we were pushing two rocks up two hills simulteaneously not 
one rock up one hill said crocker now a professor at georgetown 
university 
