<TEXT>
here is the text of soviet president mikhail s 
gorbachevs decree banning firearms sales in lithuania and ordering 
residents to turn in their guns the text transmitted in russian 
by the official news agency tass was translated by the associated 
press 
</TEXT>
<TEXT>
the ussr presidents decree on extra measures to protect the 
rights of soviet citizens and the sovereignty of the ussr on 
the territory of the lithuanian ssr 
contrary to the resolution adopted by congress of peoples 
deputies of march 15 the lithuanian parliament and government 
continue passing bills violating the rights of the soviet citizens 
and the sovereignity of the soviet union 
in connection with this i decree 
1 the ussr council of ministers the executive bodies and 
local councils of lithuanian ssr the lawenforcement organs are 
to ensure the observance of the federal constitution and laws and 
protect the rights and legitimate interests of the soviet citizens 
living or staying in lithuanian ssr 
2 kgb border forces are to take essential measures to tighten 
up security on the soviet border in lithuanian ssr to halt all 
unlawful actions violating soviet border legislation 
3 the federal governments resolution no 646 of july 23 1975 
on the acquisition accounting and keeping of hunting rifles is to 
be temporarily suspended and the sale of hunting weapons is to be 
banned for the same period in the republic citizens living in 
lithuanian ssr are within the next seven days to hand in all 
their weapons to the lawenforcement bodies for temporary keeping 
the ussr interior ministry is to seize such weapons in cases of 
refusal to turn them in the defense ministry is to receive from 
lawenforcement organs the weapons seized from citizens and ensure 
their safekeeping 
4 the foreign ministry and the interior ministry are to tighten 
control over issuance of entrance visas to foreigners and over the 
permission for foreigners to visit the lithuanian ssr 
the interior ministry and the ussr procurators office are 
to take all essential measures to suppress violations by foreigners 
staying in lithuanian ssr of the regulations concerning the stay 
of foreign nationals all the way to their deportation in keeping 
with the ussr law on the legal status of foreign nationals in 
the ussr 
5 the decree becomes effective immediately after signing 
</TEXT>
</DOC>

