rejected an initial prosecution offer of 40 years in return for a 
guilty plea 
under the agreement finally reached he would face a maximum 10 
years in prison on the single conspiracy count but is unlikely to 
serve that long burstyn said 
theres no time limit in the agreement but i believe hell 
serve no more than 2 years the attorney said 
