<TEXT>
lord rothschild the millionaire banker and 
decorated world war ii intelligence agent has died in london his 
wife said in a statement wednesday he was 79 
lady rothschild said her husband died tuesday she did not 
reveal the cause of death or give any other details rothschilds 
secretary refused to say whether he had been ill or where he died 
lord rothschild was born nathaniel mayer victor rothschild on 
oct 31 1910 into the famous family of germanjewish coin 
collectors who founded a banking dynasty 
lord rothschild was the head of the english wing of the family 
baron guy de rothschild is head of the french branch 
after studying sciences english and french at cambridge he 
went on to become a professor in the zoology department and was 
recognized as one of the worlds leading experts on spermatozoa 
he succeeded his uncle as the 3rd baron rothschild in 1937 
taking his seat in the house of lords the unelected upper chamber 
of parliament as a member of the labor party in the early 1970s 
he served as an adviser to conservative prime minister edward heath 
during world war ii rothschild served as a senior officer with 
mi5 the british counterespionage service 
britain awarded rothschild the george medal for bravery in world 
war ii for defusing german bombs he also received the american 
legion of merit for his wartime efforts 
in 1986 rothschild sent a letter to the daily telegraph urging 
mi5 to state publicly that it had unequivocal evidence 
disproving rumors that he was the fifth man in the infamous 
soviet spy ring formed by guy burgess kim philby donald maclean 
and anthony blunt 
rothschild in his student days at cambridge university was a 
member of the elite debating society known as the apostles as were 
burgess and blunt rothschild and blunt who became art adviser to 
queen elizabeth ii remained friends in adult life 
in his letter rothschild said there had been innuendos since 
1981 that he was the fifth man 
british press reports said the unequivocal evidence rothschild 
referred to was a secret 1962 meeting in london when he finally 
nailed philby as a soviet agent philby a former british 
intelligence officer was then a beirutbased journalist 
prime minister margaret thatcher said the government had no 
evidence that rothschild was ever a soviet agent 
the rothschild family has a reputation for generosity 
especially toward israel 
an orthodox jew lord rothschild was awarded an honorary degree 
from tel aviv university in 1971 for the advancement of science 
education and the economy of israel it was followed in 1975 by 
an honorary degree from jerusalems hebrew university 
he was also an accomplished cricket player golfer jazz 
pianist writer and businessman 
lady rothschilds statement said a private funeral will be held 
but did not say when or where she said there would be a memorial 
service later 
besides his wife the former tessa mayor lord rothschild is 
survived by their son james and their two daughters emma and 
victoria he is also survived by a son jacob and two daughters 
sarah and miranda from his first marriage which ended in 1945 
jacob a trustee of the national gallery is the heir to the 
peerage becoming the 4th baron rothschild 
</TEXT>
