swearing to defend the gains of the revolution that brought 
them to power in 1979 
if the peaceful transfer of power and national reconciliation 
are not achieved its legitimate to protect those who have 
propelled the social economic and judicial transformations that 
now benefit most of the people national assembly president 
carlos nunez said 
