an interview that such legislation exists but suggested that the 
lithuanian parliament will not approve it such stupidity will 
get us nowhere he said of the proposal 
the soviet deputies whose group is called soyuz appealed to 
gorbachev to use the new powers of the presidency to impose direct 
rule on lithuania tass said 
