that makes teenagers smoke not stadium billboards or magazine ads 
yes she said the regulators have won many recent rounds 
including a virtual ban on smoking aboard airliners and yes for 
those in the industry its certainly a difficult climate 
but smokings decline in this country should not be exaggerated 
ms dawson said 
if its something that 50 million people still do im not 
sure that i buy that its been desocialized she said 
