the cold war thaw brings a dilemma for hollywoods 
scriptwriters whom are we going to use for villains those 
ruthless agents of the evil empire look like pussycats now 
movies such as to russia with love and the spy who came in 
from the cold would be robbed of their immediacy if filmed today 
