the entry requirements are few 
you have to be an active downhill skier you must be 70 years 
of age says lloyd t lambert founder of the 70plus ski club 
you pay 5 for a lifetime membership 
the claims more than 5500 members across the country 
im not that speedy any more but weve got some really 
