senior citizens are staying in shape on the slopes in droves 
these days and the trend shows no signs of slowing with older 
americans keener than ever to stay active skiing is an ideal way 
to exercise through the winter 
its caught on now to where it membership has grown 75 
percent a year said bill vandersluin 59 spokesman for the over 
