chevrolet camaro 
when automakers make police cars they swap out some standard 
equipment and replace it with components more suited to rugged 
driving 
in the caprice chevrolet offers an optional 57liter engine in 
place of the standard 5liter engine and larger tires for 
highspeed driving a variety of options also is available so law 
