the local agency equips the vehicles with among other things 
radios cages separating the front and rear seats and sirens 
the mustang and the camaro which can reach 100 mph much quicker 
than their larger cousins are expected to attract state highway 
patrols which might use them to prowl freeways for speeders 
because of their size fullsize caprice and crown victoria cars 
are expected to remain popular with taxi companies and police 
departments which require fourdoors and door space for occupants 
who frequently must get in and out of the vehicle 
