the popular nutrisystem diet program has come 
under fire from 19 south florida women who say in separate lawsuits 
that they have suffered gall bladder damage from the rapid 
weightloss plan 
the company defends its program as safe and suggests the gall 
bladder problems are coincidental 
all but two of the women ages 17 to 60 have had gall bladder 
