jurors began deliberating today on 
whether joseph hazelwood was a reckless drunk or a prudent tanker 
captain conflicting portrayals by the prosecution and defense in 
a full day of intense summations 
superior court judge karl johnstone turned the 7weekold 
criminal case in the nations worst oil spill over to the jury late 
